  "updated_summary": "In a dark, icy cavern illuminated by an eerie blue light, the Elderly Man cries out in distress, warning that \"The mischievous brats are attacking!\" The Calabash Brothers, standing defiantly atop a cloud-like formation, raise their fists. The Boy, holding a dark purple gourd, declares, \"Don't panic! Watch me deal with their bones!\" and demands the return of his brother, threatening to \"breathe fire!\" and \"spit water!\" A rabbit-like creature warns the brothers against causing trouble. The Boy accuses his brother of being possessed and helping demons, while his brother retorts, \"YOU are the demons! I'm mom's good baby!\" The Elderly Man pleads for him to wake up, but the Brother threatens him. The scene shifts to reveal the Regal Woman and the Crab-Like Monster. The Regal Woman cackles and utters \"Naniyo!\" and \"Ni zhen shi hao qi!\" as the Calabash Brothers confront them, leaping through flames and ice. The Regal Woman emits a red beam, striking the Boy, who falls but remains resolute, activating the gourd to unleash a blue energy blast that shatters a glowing bowl, freeing a child encased in ice. The Boy uses a glowing pink leaf to shatter the ice, freeing the child. The Regal Woman, frustrated, utters \"Mmm...\" and \"Ni zhe ge hun...\" as the Boy and his brother stand triumphantly, while the Regal Woman and Crab-Like Monster retreat. The Boy declares, \"I'm going to show you something powerful!\" The Serpentine Creature charges her attack, emitting a red beam that strikes the Boy. The Crab-Like Monster roars, and the Serpentine Creature asks, \"What are you doing, kid?\" The Boy wields a Golden Object, emitting a blue beam that strikes the dark purple gourd, causing a purple explosion. He then unleashes a pink energy blast. The Serpentine Creature emits another red beam, striking the Boy, who falls. The Child in Ice cries out to his mother, the Serpentine Creature, who tells him to \"quickly punish him!\" The Crab-Like Monster warns the \"Sixth brother\" about fighting the Boy head-on. The Boy, on the ground, confidently raises the Golden Object, chanting, \"As I wish, as I wish, according to my will, quickly manifest! Quickly manifest!\" He emits a blue beam that shatters a large, ornate Glowing Bowl, releasing the Child in Ice. The Boy uses the Glowing Pink Leaf to shatter the ice encasing the child. The child, now free, asks, \"Ah! What's happening!\". The scene ends with the Boy standing triumphantly, the child free, and the Serpentine Creature and Crab-Like Monster retreating, as magical energy sounds continue."
